node->nvm

version manager

- commands
    - ls-remote: displays available versions
        - --lts: only lts-versions
    - ls: displays locally installed versions
    - use <version>: sets current version to <version>
        - e.g. nvm use default (alias 'default' currently refers to LTS v18.17.1)
    - alias default <version>: sets default version
    - current: displays currently used version

- SEE ALSO
    - github.com/nvm-sh/nvm
    - freecodecamp.org/news/node-version-manager-nvm-install-guide/
